					<ul>
						<li>Multiple writing styles to choose from</li>
						<li>Directly download as a PDF</li>
						<li>Advanced options to select which traits to prioritize</li>
						<li>Adaptable to use in many contexts</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="column">
					<h3>Use LOR Generator Anywhere</h3>
